content.title: Creative Power
content.song:
Creative Power is strong.
Beautiful World!

content.title: The World is a Canvas
content.song:
Verse 1:
The world is a canvas, so let's paint it bright
Let's fill it with beauty and make it alight
Let's bring out the colors and make them shine bright
And show the world what we can do tonight

Chorus: 
We can create a masterpiece, with our hands and our hearts 
We can make something beautiful, that will never part 
We can show the world what we can do, when we come together as one 
Let's paint the world with love and light, until the day is done. 

Verse 2: 
Let's take all our dreams and turn them into art 
Let's bring out the beauty that lies in our hearts 
Let's show everyone what we have to give 
And share our love so that others may live. 

 Chorus: 
We can create a masterpiece, with our hands and our hearts 
We can make something beautiful, that will never part 
We can show the world what we can do, when we come together as one 
Let's paint the world with love and light, until the day is done.

content.title: The Power of Imagination
content.song:
Verse 1:  												  	  	  	  	  	  	  	  	  	  	   

The power of imagination is within us all,   	   	   	   	   	   
It takes us to places where dreams become real,    
Where anything is possible if you just believe.    
So let your mind wander and explore what you feel.   
 

Chorus:     

Take a journey of discovery to find your true self,     
Unlock your potential and reach for something else.     
Unleash your creativity and let it take flight,     
For there are no limits to what you can ignite.    


Verse 2:    

Open up your heart to see what lies inside,    
Unlock its secrets and explore its pride.    
Find courage in yourself to take on any task,    
For nothing is impossible if you just ask.    

                                                                                         
Chorus:     

Take a journey of discovery to find your true self,     
Unlock your potential and reach for something else.     
Unleash your creativity and let it take flight,     
For there are no limits to what you can ignite.

content.title: A New Dawn
content.song:
Verse 1:       
The sun rises on a new dawn today        
A chance for us all to start anew       
To leave behind all of yesterday        
And look forward to all that awaits us too        

Chorus:         
Let us embrace this new day ahead        
With hope in our hearts for what lies ahead        
Let us be brave in facing whatever comes        
For this new dawn brings promise of things yet undone        

Verse 2:         
Let us be kind in all that we do        
And strive for justice in everything too        
Let us be strong when times get tough        
And never forget how far we've come thus far       

Chorus:         
Let us embrace this new day ahead        
With hope in our hearts for what lies ahead        
Let us be brave in facing whatever comes        
For this new dawn brings promise of things yet undone

content.title: Bohemian Rhapsody
content.song:
Is this the real life? 
Is this just fantasy? 
Caught in a landslide, 
No escape from reality. 
Open your eyes, 
Look up to the skies and see, 
I'm just a poor boy, I need no sympathy, 
Because I'm easy come, easy go, 
Little high, little low. 
Anyway the wind blows doesn't really matter to me, to me. 
Mama, just killed a man, 
Put a gun against his head, 
Pulled my trigger now he's dead. 
Mama life had just begun, 
But now I've gone and thrown it all away.  
Mama ooh (any way the wind blows),  
Didn't mean to make you cry.  
If I'm not back again this time tomorrow  
Carry on carry on as if nothing really matters.  

Too late my time has come,  
Sends shivers down my spine body's aching all the time.  
Goodbye everybody I've got to go Gotta leave you all behind and face the truth.  

Mama ooh (any way the wind blows),  
I don't want to die.  
Sometimes wish I'd never been born at all.
